with the circumstances of our life, that no matter what brought us into this conversation, no matter the joy we find ourselves in or the grief we find ourselves in or the sorrow or shame we find ourselves in, we really do believe that there is hope available, that just because something's happened to us or we've done something in our past or even our present, there really can be a different future in you.

