09:08.162 --> 09:17.153
They were using someone's body to have a temporary experience that was transactional, but they didn't need to know their name, they didn't need to know their heart, they didn't need to know their story.

09:17.253 --> 09:20.657
It was just a one-night stand.

09:22.219 --> 09:22.780
