14:57.362 --> 15:01.447
The reason that Paul says this is because he knows how powerful sex is.

15:02.348 --> 15:03.890
Paul is saying that sexual sin

15:04.002 --> 15:04.603
is unique.

15:05.324 --> 15:06.225
It's different.

15:06.245 --> 15:09.310
