15:16.280 --> 15:26.274
He says, flee because of the kinds of bonds that we talked about in week one, that welding ourselves to someone outside the covenant of marriage has permanent consequences.

15:26.374 --> 15:27.495
It doesn't mean there isn't grace.

15:27.836 --> 15:32.082
It doesn't mean that there isn't hope, but we cannot believe the cultural lie that it doesn't matter.

15:32.866 --> 15:35.169
We aren't scared of a sunset, right?

15:35.189 --> 15:40.998
When we sit back and appreciate a sunset in our life, we know that we're at a safe distance from that heat.

15:41.078 --> 15:41.959
